IV. RESULTS AND DISCUSSIONS
The proposed AI-based personalized mental health support system was implemented and evaluated using a prototype environment with student users as the primary target group. The system successfully completed all three functional stages: psychological assessment, personalized AI assistance, and stress-relief engagement.
During the psychological assessment phase as shown in figure 1, users were able to complete structured questionnaires without difficulty, and the system effectively generated individualized psychological profiles based on their responses. The preprocessing and encryption mechanisms ensured secure handling of sensitive user data, maintaining privacy and data integrity throughout the process.
In the personalized AI assistant phase, the system demonstrated the ability to adapt conversational tone, response style, and support strategies according to the user’s psychological profile. Users reported improved comfort in expressing emotions and engaging in conversations with the AI assistant. The assistant effectively provided stress-coping suggestions, emotional reassurance, and motivational guidance based on user interactions.
The stress-relief and engagement phase showed positive user participation, with increased interaction time in relaxation activities and games. Users indicated that these activities helped reduce immediate stress levels and improved overall mood. Feedback analysis suggested that the integration of entertainment-based modules enhanced user engagement and contributed to sustained system usage.
User Input	AI Assistant Response	Profile Context
"I have three assignments due tomorrow and I haven't started any of them. I feel overwhelmed."	"It sounds like you're dealing with a lot right now. Let's break this down together. Which assignment is worth the most points or has the nearest deadline? Sometimes focusing on one task at a time makes things feel more manageable. Would it help to create a quick priority list?"	High stress sensitivity, prefers structured guidance
"I don't feel like talking today."	"That's completely okay. You don't have to talk if you're not ready. I'm here whenever you need me. Would you like to try one of the relaxation exercises instead, or would you prefer some quiet time?"	Introverted profile, respects autonomy

      
